   <text><body><seg type="excerpt" xml:id="ex14022023-10-11-105324" status="reviewed">phyi<lb n="1a2"/> tsha<lb n="1a3"/> 103<lb n="1a4"/> <rs type="work" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:4575"><rs type="work" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:3711">mngon rtogs rgyan</rs> gyi 'grel bshad 'thad pa'i <lb n="1a5"/>'od 'bar</rs></seg>
      <seg type="excerpt" xml:id="ex14022025-03-31-25" status="reviewed"> gzhi shes kyi <abbr>mtshan nyid</abbr> la gsum las ¦ 
             rtog pas btags pa dgag pa ni | nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas dang gnyen po gzhi shes kyi <abbr>mtshan nyid</abbr> <note type="gloss"><rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:3886">se</rs> <rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:3807">'bre</rs></note><note type="editorial">"Se" is understood to refer to be the author's teacher dge bshes Se dmar ba (ID:3886), but it could also be Jo bo Se btsun (ID:6763). "'Bre" is understodd to refer to 'Bre shes rab 'bar (ID:3807) but could also refer to gTsang pa 'bre sgur (ID:3872)</note> gzhi <abbr>thams cad</abbr> gang zag gi bdag med dang | gang zag gi bdag dang gzung ba rang bzhin med <lb n="24b3"/> pa tsam dang bdag mtha' dag skye ba med par mngon sum du rtogs pa'o zhes so |</seg>
             
           
            <seg type="excerpt" xml:id="ex14022024-10-21-15-34" status="finalized">         
            'di la <rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:unnamed_reference" ref="db:3805">kha 1</rs> <note type="gloss"><rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:3805">gnyal</rs></note> nyan rang la chos kyi bdag med rtogs pa yod pas de mi rigs so zhes so ||</seg>

            des na thabs la khyad yod kyi shes rab la khyad med do zhes so ||
            
            skyon de ni med de <seg type="excerpt" xml:id="ex1142-10502023-08-22" status="reviewed" ana="corpusmd:colophon"><milestone unit="section" n="Colophon (184a1-185a4)"/>          
               <rs type="work" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:4575"><rs type="work" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:3711">shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i man ngag gi bstan bcos mngon par rtogs pa'i rgyan</rs> ces <lb n="185a3"/>bya ba'i 'grel bshad 'thad pa'i 'od 'bar</rs> zhes bya ba | shes bya'i nam mkha' la blo gros kyi dkyil 'khor rgyas shing | legs smra'i 'od kyis phas rgol mun pa'i smag rum sel bar byed pa <rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:3884">shAkya'i dge slong rigs par <lb n="185a4"/>smra ba shes rab 'od zer</rs> gyis sbyar ba rdzogs so || × ||dag cing snyoms pa <rs type="person" ana="corpusmd:named_reference" ref="db:4576">shes rab 'bum</rs> gyis bris | dge'o || ||</seg>
